detaileddescription.para:
This function is, by definition, MSW-specific. It can be used to access pre-defined shell directories not covered by the existing methods of this class, e.g.: #ifdef__WXMSW__
//getthelocationoffileswaitingtobeburnedonaCD
wxStringcdburnArea=
wxStandardPaths::MSWGetShellDir(CSIDL_CDBURN_AREA);
#endif//__WXMSW__
